===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|sory|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|sarig|sāriġ|feeling or expressing grief, sorry, grieved, sorrowful, sad, mournful, bitter|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|sairagaz||sad|lang=gem-pro}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{recons|sayǝw-||hard, rough, painful|lang=ine-pro}}. Cognate with {{etyl|nds|-}} {{term|serig||sick, scabby|lang=nds}}, {{etyl|de|-}} dialectal {{term|sehrig||sore, sad, painful|lang=de}}. More at {{l|en|sore}}.

