{{en-adj|sorri|er}}

# {{context|of a person}} [[regretful|Regretful]] for an action; [[grieved]] or [[sadden]]ed, especially by the loss of something or someone.
#: ''I am '''sorry''' I stepped on your toes. It was an accident.''
